description: Creates a group profile in Amazon DataZone.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: A unique, case-sensitive identifier that is provided to ensure the idempotency of the request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon DataZone domain in which the group profile is created.

parameters.name: groupIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier of the group for which the group profile is created.

nested_items.name: domainId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the Amazon DataZone domain in which the group profile is created.

nested_items.name: groupName
nested_items.description: The name of the group for which group profile is created.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The identifier of the group profile.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the group profile.
